                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Port of Spain</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-04-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 27, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Russell informs Mr. Root that the plenipotentiary appointed by Colombia to
                    arrange with Venezuelan plenipotentiary a treaty of navigation frontiers and
                    frontier and transit commerce arrived about three weeks ago, and requested to be
                    received by the Acting President in a formal audience. Mr. Russell states that
                    the Government replied that the Colombian plenipotentiary could not be received
                    in accordance with the terms of the protocol of last December until the treaty
                    had been signed and put into execution. The Colombian plenipotentiary insisted
                    until finally the Government of Venezuela stated that it could have no further
                    relations with him and that Colombian Government must send some one else.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
